M|rules|title: Use SWR for Automatic Deduplication
M|rules|impact: MEDIUM-HIGH
M|rules|impactDescription: automatic deduplication
M|rules|tags: client, swr, deduplication, data-fetching
M|rules|SWR enables request deduplication, caching, and revalidation across component instances.
M|rules|**Incorrect (no deduplication, each instance fetches):**
M|rules|```tsx
M|rules|function UserList() {
M|rules|const [users, setUsers] = useState([])
M|rules|useEffect(() => {
M|rules|fetch('/api/users')
M|rules|.then(r => r.json())
M|rules|.then(setUsers)
M|rules|}, [])
M|rules|}
M|rules|```
M|rules|**Correct (multiple instances share one request):**
M|rules|```tsx
M|rules|import useSWR from 'swr'
M|rules|function UserList() {
M|rules|const { data: users } = useSWR('/api/users', fetcher)
M|rules|}
M|rules|```
M|rules|**For immutable data:**
M|rules|```tsx
M|rules|import { useImmutableSWR } from '@/lib/swr'
M|rules|function StaticContent() {
M|rules|const { data } = useImmutableSWR('/api/config', fetcher)
M|rules|}
M|rules|```
M|rules|**For mutations:**
M|rules|```tsx
M|rules|import { useSWRMutation } from 'swr/mutation'
M|rules|function UpdateButton() {
M|rules|const { trigger } = useSWRMutation('/api/user', updateUser)
M|rules|return <button onClick={() => trigger()}>Update</button>
M|rules|}
M|rules|```
M|rules|Reference: [https://swr.vercel.app](https://swr.vercel.app)